From fdc3c9c5e195bca976cdeed34f7d8986c14ef6fb Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Potin Lai <potin.lai@quantatw.com>
Date: Sun, 23 Mar 2025 11:03:46 +0800
Subject: [PATCH 4/4] configurations: nvidia_gb200_io_board: Use external
 sensor service for temperature monitoring

Due to a hardware design limitation, the port temperature is only
accessible via pldmtool.

Switch Backend NIC die temperature and port temperature monitoring to
external sensor service, this allows a other service to update sensor
readings.

Signed-off-by: Potin Lai <potin.lai@quantatw.com>
Change-Id: Iee90f1b75cf3a7ddabcd5f5cd640897431d4a6ea
---
 configurations/nvidia_gb200_io_board.json | 90 ++++++++++++++++++-----
 1 file changed, 70 insertions(+), 20 deletions(-)

